Prof Krash 's notes were clear and explains concepts in great detail, plus he's funny too, which makes the material much more enjoyable. GO TO TUTORIALS, my TA is excellent and explaining the questions very well. DO AS MANY PAST MIDTERMS/EXAMS AS POSSIBLE? and you will do fine
